-=The Last Fantasy=-
-=The Last Fantasy=-

3
00:00:04,988 --> 00:00:07,320
Hold nothing back! Leave it all on the floor!

4
00:00:07,490 --> 00:00:10,425
-How much time we got? -We've got fifteen minutes tops!

5
00:00:10,593 --> 00:00:12,424
Just enough time to get in and out!

6
00:00:13,430 --> 00:00:15,421
All right, let's do this thing!

7
00:00:31,114 --> 00:00:32,809
Are you ready now, Clark?

8
00:00:32,983 --> 00:00:35,611
Yeah. I forgot to press the record button. Sorry.

9
00:00:36,486 --> 00:00:38,351
So, Mr. Luthor...

10
00:00:38,521 --> 00:00:41,820
...any more secret construction projects at LuthorCorp like Level 3?

11
00:00:42,025 --> 00:00:43,652
Please, call me Lex.

12
00:00:44,194 --> 00:00:46,662
-Lex, are you gonna answer my question? -Chloe.

13
00:00:46,830 --> 00:00:49,594
-What? -It's okay, Clark.

14
00:00:49,766 --> 00:00:52,326
"Our critics are our friends. They show us our faults."

15
00:00:52,936 --> 00:00:55,370
Benjamin Franklin.

16
00:00:55,939 --> 00:00:57,497
Excuse me, Mr. Luthor...

17
00:00:57,674 --> 00:01:00,700
-...your father's on the phone. -I need to get this.

18
00:01:02,178 --> 00:01:05,113
I'll take it in the conservatory.

19
00:01:06,016 --> 00:01:09,315
I look forward to resuming our verbal judo.

20
00:01:17,460 --> 00:01:20,793
-All right, boys, this is the big one! -Yeah! Let's do it!

21
00:01:20,964 --> 00:01:22,795
Let's go!

22
00:01:22,966 --> 00:01:26,925
I wonder if he's really taking a call or if he's just trying to avoid me?

23
00:01:27,103 --> 00:01:29,367
Wow, that's really cool.

24
00:01:29,572 --> 00:01:31,870
Do you think it's real?

25
00:01:36,946 --> 00:01:39,073
Chloe?

26
00:01:40,683 --> 00:01:42,810
Chloe.

27
00:01:50,093 --> 00:01:52,653
Okay. The vault's in the wall behind the bookcase.

28
00:01:52,829 --> 00:01:55,525
-How do you know? -I've got my sources.

29
00:01:55,698 --> 00:01:59,532
-He was doing one of the housekeepers. -Oh, yeah.

30
00:02:19,923 --> 00:02:22,448
-We got five minutes, let's move it! -Let's do it!

31
00:02:23,693 --> 00:02:27,151
That's it, boys, come on. It's payday!

32
00:02:38,541 --> 00:02:41,032
One minute!

33
00:02:42,245 --> 00:02:45,146
-Come on, let's go! -I only got one arm.

34
00:02:45,915 --> 00:02:48,110
Yeah!

35
00:02:49,619 --> 00:02:52,645
Time's up! Let's move it! Let's go!

36
00:02:53,156 --> 00:02:55,556
You can't just go snooping around someone's house.

37
00:02:55,725 --> 00:02:59,889
Clark, it's a mansion. It's designed for snooping.

38
00:03:00,230 --> 00:03:02,721
Okay, fine. We'll go and wait in the library...

39
00:03:02,899 --> 00:03:06,357
...for Lex to officially blow us off.

40
00:03:06,903 --> 00:03:10,532
-I'll put the camera away. -Okay, I'm gonna go get my bag.

41
00:03:13,776 --> 00:03:15,744
Hey, what's going on?

42
00:03:19,516 --> 00:03:21,006
Chloe, run!

43
00:03:46,376 --> 00:03:49,140
Move it! Let's move it!

44
00:03:50,013 --> 00:03:51,002
Clark!

45
00:03:52,015 --> 00:03:53,380
Chloe.

46
00:03:53,550 --> 00:03:55,484
Clark!

47
00:04:05,328 --> 00:04:06,352
Chloe!

48
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:04,000
翻译:龙猫，versus，点点姑娘，颀觎 校对:岁月倒影，TYY

49
00:00:04,988 --> 00:00:07,320
别犹豫！动手要干净利落！

50
00:00:07,490 --> 00:00:10,425
- 我们有多少时间？ - 最多十五分钟！

51
00:00:10,593 --> 00:00:12,424
刚好够来回一趟！

52
00:00:13,430 --> 00:00:15,421
好，我们干吧！

53
00:00:31,114 --> 00:00:32,809
这回准备好了吧，克拉克？

54
00:00:32,983 --> 00:00:35,611
是，我刚才忘了按记录键 不好意思

55
00:00:36,486 --> 00:00:38,351
那么，卢瑟先生…

56
00:00:38,521 --> 00:00:41,820
…卢瑟公司还有更多像第三层那样 秘密建设的项目吗？

57
00:00:42,025 --> 00:00:43,652
拜托，叫我莱克斯

58
00:00:44,194 --> 00:00:46,662
- 莱克斯，你会回答我的问题吗？ - 克罗伊

59
00:00:46,830 --> 00:00:49,594
- 什么？ - 没事，克拉克

60
00:00:49,766 --> 00:00:52,326
“…批评者是我们的朋友 他们指出我们的错误”

61
00:00:52,936 --> 00:00:55,370
本杰明・富兰克林的名言吧

62
00:00:55,939 --> 00:00:57,497
打扰了，卢瑟先生…

63
00:00:57,674 --> 00:01:00,700
- …您父亲来电 - 我得接这电话

64
00:01:02,178 --> 00:01:05,113
我到花房去接电话

65
00:01:06,016 --> 00:01:09,315
我期待继续与你唇枪舌战

66
00:01:17,460 --> 00:01:20,793
- 好的，兄弟们，这是笔大买卖！ - 是啊！我们干吧！

67
00:01:20,964 --> 00:01:22,795
走吧！

68
00:01:22,966 --> 00:01:26,925
我怀疑他是真的在接电话 还是要躲我？

69
00:01:27,103 --> 00:01:29,367
哇，这个真酷

70
00:01:29,572 --> 00:01:31,870
你认为它是真品吗？

71
00:01:36,946 --> 00:01:39,073
克罗伊？

72
00:01:40,683 --> 00:01:42,810
克罗伊

73
00:01:50,093 --> 00:01:52,653
好的，金库在墙里面，书架后面

74
00:01:52,829 --> 00:01:55,525
- 你怎么知道？ - 我自有消息来源

75
00:01:55,698 --> 00:01:59,532
- 他勾搭过这的一个佣人 - 哦，爽啊

76
00:02:19,923 --> 00:02:22,448
- 我们有五分钟，赶紧动手吧！ - 我们干吧！

77
00:02:23,693 --> 00:02:27,151
就是这些，兄弟们，今天发财了！

78
00:02:38,541 --> 00:02:41,032
剩一分钟了！

79
00:02:42,245 --> 00:02:45,146
- 快啊，走了！ - 我只有一只手

80
00:02:49,619 --> 00:02:52,645
时间到了！走啊！快走！

81
00:02:53,156 --> 00:02:55,556
你不能在人家房子里到处窥探

82
00:02:55,725 --> 00:02:59,889
克拉克，这么大的宅邸 当然就是用来被窥探的

83
00:03:00,230 --> 00:03:02,721
好吧，行 我们去书房等吧…

84
00:03:02,899 --> 00:03:06,357
…等着莱克斯正式宣布放我们鸽子

85
00:03:06,903 --> 00:03:10,532
- 我把相机收了 - 好，我要去拿我的包

86
00:03:13,776 --> 00:03:15,744
嘿，这是怎么回事？

87
00:03:19,516 --> 00:03:21,006
克罗伊，快跑啊！

88
00:03:46,376 --> 00:03:49,140
跑啊！快跑啊！

89
00:03:50,013 --> 00:03:51,002
克拉克！

90
00:03:52,015 --> 00:03:53,380
克罗伊

91
00:03:53,550 --> 00:03:55,484
克拉克！

92
00:04:05,328 --> 00:04:06,352
克罗伊！

